+ * authorization.ts — Bitwise RBAC Permission Gate
+ * Task: agenthub.internal.task_051
+ *
+ * Permissions bitmask (Unix-style):
+ *   LIST   = 1   (0001)
+ *   READ   = 2   (0010)
